    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>迪迪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >类型：生存 / 动作 / 合作<br><br>描述：你准备好摧毁迪迪豪宅中的黑暗派对了吗？召集你的战友50 Cent和埃米纳姆，终结迪迪的肮脏勾当，击败他并拯救通过欺骗手段积累财富的贾斯汀B。<br><br>在这款游戏中，你不仅要面对迪迪，还要对抗保护他豪宅的明星军队。迪迪的手下包括强大而有影响力的明星，他们每个人都准备好为捍卫豪宅与你战斗。但有了战友埃米纳姆和50 Cent，你们将全力以赴，赢得这场艰苦的战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272140/extras/6787a8f629c162238597de31835455a8.poster.avif?t=1751887200\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272140/extras/6787a8f629c162238597de31835455a8.webm?t=1751887200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272140/extras/6787a8f629c162238597de31835455a8.mp4?t=1751887200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>从迪迪的豪宅到一个大型赌场，再到隐藏迪迪秘密金库的地方，这个充满动作的冒险将带领你完成艰难的任务，解开小谜题，努力拯救贾斯汀B。与朋友一起进行合作模式时，你需要运用战术智慧来击败满是明星的敌军，破坏迪迪的计划。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272140/extras/0c8027edbdf842441c74de50d959d55a.poster.avif?t=1751887200\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272140/extras/0c8027edbdf842441c74de50d959d55a.webm?t=1751887200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272140/extras/0c8027edbdf842441c74de50d959d55a.mp4?t=1751887200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你和你的战友能否在迪迪的神秘世界中追求正义，克服遇到的所有障碍？阻止迪迪，拯救贾斯汀B，并结束这场混乱的派对！</p>",
